label: Aboutus
text: Get a Free Quote Zealousinformatics.com is a platform which offers a wide range of data services and solutions ranging from data collection tools design data collection data cleaning data entry data analysis data visualization to comprehensive report writing for either individuals institutions or organizations. In order to perform all this tasks Zealousinformatics.com has experienced economics Statistics Econometrics Mathematics computing and Information Technology professionals who are knowledgeable with data science models and theories that are used to solve day to day data problems. To ensure high quality work We use better and stronger data systems and Statistical software or tools such as RSTATASPSSEVIEWS EXCEL for data analysis and Epinfo Epidata for data entry Open Data Kit (ODK) for mobile data collection and database administration using SQLite and SQL. With Statistics Economics Mathematics and Econometrics knowledge and enhancing with Statistical software and databases we are able to handle large datasets by exploring big data carry out cross validation and effective statistical analysis and interpretation of results we are able to learn from data and extract meaningful information for effective decision making. At Zealousinformatics.com we work as a team and sure that we deliver tasks in time and also we ensure quality well done work as expected by our clients. So it is not a “one man task” we work together to ensure a success to your project be it academic paper Monitoring and evaluation report or end year report we are faithful to our clients by honoring agreements and high quality work. So what do you need done? About Zealousinformatics.com
